{"word":"ἀποθήκη","slug":"ἀποθήκη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀποϑήϰη, ης, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀποτίθημι\">ἀποτίθημι</a></el>] ‘a place for storage’, <b><i>storehouse,</i></b> so in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> of various kinds of depositories including facilities for storage of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σῖτος\">σῖτος</a></el> (grain) and <el>ἀγαϑά</el> (good things) <b><a href='B:490 12:18'>Lk 12:18</a>;</b> specifically <b><i>granary</i> <a href='B:470 3:12'>Mt 3:12</a>; <a href='B:470 13:30'>13:30</a>; <a href='B:490 3:17'>Lk 3:17</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:470 6:26'>Mt 6:26</a>; <a href='B:490 12:24'>Lk 12:24</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ταμεῖον\">ταμεῖον</a></el>). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπόθεσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀποθησαυρίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}